# BidPazar Web Tech Stack

## Core Technologies
- Next.js 15.2+
- React 19+
- TypeScript 5+
- TailwindCSS 3.4+
- Socket.io Client 4.8+
- Simple-Peer 9.11+ (WebRTC)

## UI Components
- Radix UI primitives
- Lucide React icons
- class-variance-authority
- clsx/tailwind-merge for class composition
- React Hook Form with Zod validation

## Development Tools
- Jest for testing
- Testing Library (React, DOM, User Event)
- ESLint 9+
- Postcss 8.4+

## Key Libraries
- axios: API requests
- cookies-next: Cookie management
- hls.js: HTTP Live Streaming
- mediasoup-client: WebRTC consumption
- react-hot-toast/sonner: Notifications
- uuid: Unique ID generation

## Project Structure
- src/
  - app/: Next.js App Router pages
  - components/: Reusable UI components
  - hooks/: Custom React hooks
  - lib/: Utility functions
  - types/: TypeScript type definitions
  - tests/: Test files

## Patterns
- Server and client components separation
- Custom hooks for shared logic
- API services for backend communication
- Context providers for state management
- Component composition
- Responsive design with Tailwind breakpoints

